entries.journal_entry_description: Ysith and Myssith have been fighting amongst themselves for a very long time, and Ysith has decided it is time to do away with a rival. She has hired you to travel to the Kkowir Forest, find Myssith in the abandoned Imperial compound, and kill her.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Ysith wants you to find her rival, Myssith, in the Kkowir Forest. Myssith is known to be working out of the abandoned Imperial installation in Kkowir.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Ysith needs you to eliminate Myssith in order for her to finally have some peace. Myssith tends to come and go but never stays away from the camp for very long.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go back to Ysith and tell her of your success in removing her rival.
